Violette FR is a French-inspired beauty collection created by self-made makeup artist and social media star Violette Serrat. Offering vegan, cruelty-free products made with clean ingredients, Violette FR is known for chic, simple beauty looks featured in Vogue, InStyle, Glamour, and Elle.

March 30, 2021 - In 2012, she was appointed as the International Makeup Designer of Dior Beauty where she became the youngest makeup designer in the brand’s history.
